window.bookSummaryJSON = "The third book in the #1 <i>New York Times</i> best-selling series from Jeff Kinney, <i>The Last Straw</i> is sure to please young readers. Greg Heffley makes a New Year's resolution to help others improve, but his brand of truthful advice doesn't go over well. Plus, Greg's dad thinks military school might be just the attitude adjustment Greg needs."; 
